Teal Marchande https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Teal_Marchande 0 Belinda Teal Marchande (born January 11, 1963) is a former American actress, best known for her role as Sheryl Rockmore on the Nickelodeon sitcom Kenan Kel. She has also guest-starred on Martin and the UPN sitcom Good News. She has not acted professionally since Kenan Kel ended in 2000. Marchande once had a relationship with Washington Redskins linebacker Ravin Caldwell. Together they have a daughter Talia Caldwell, who played college basketball at the University of California, Berkeley. They reside in Los Angeles.
